=== Infrastructure_Comparison ===
Compare it to:
• Building age verification for every website
• Maintaining massive databases of identity documents
• Enforcing bans across millions of websites
• Dealing with VPNs and proxies
• Managing security risks of centralized ID databases

Parent education infrastructure is simpler, more effective, and doesn't create surveillance risks.

