=== Irresponsible_Parents ===
True. And age verification laws don't fix that.

A parent who won't install parental controls also won't prevent their child from using a VPN. A parent who isn't involved won't benefit from age bans either.

The difference: our solution doesn't create surveillance infrastructure that can be misused. It empowers the parents who DO care without endangering everyone's privacy.

